name: WFO: Unstable Unidentified Flying Object
description:
This is WFO: Unstable Unidentified Flying Object!

Yeah, yeah, the title is a really dumb wordplay joke, but that's the kind of mood I was in when I made this thing, alright? This was made for the one-button game jam for a class of mine, which means- you guessed it: this game is played entirely with one button! The spacebar to be exact.

Controls:

Press space bar to switch the direction your spaceship is flying. (This will also happen when you hit the edge of the screen)

Avoid the asteroids and get to the end of the level!

Music credits:

Moon Theme from DuckTales Remastered

Super Mario World Game Over Theme

Win Screen song by Louie Zong (Didn't include the title because it's a spoiler)

Speaking of spoilers: PLEASE DO NOT SPOIL THE EPIC TWIST ENDING
